juniSysClockAgent.name: juniSysClockAgent

revisions.description: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Added an indicator to stratum number that no stratum is set. Added traps for significant NTP state changes. Added replacement clock offset and frequency error objects with DisplaySting syntax.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniSysClockAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniSysClockAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the system clock component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniSysClockAgentV1.name: juniSysClockAgentV1
juniSysClockAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the system clock component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the system clock component was supported in JUNOSe 4.0 system
        releases.
juniSysClockAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the system clock application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when NTP trap support was added.

juniSysClockAgentV2.name: juniSysClockAgentV2
juniSysClockAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the system clock component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the system clock component was supported in early JUNOSe 4.1
        and 5.0 system releases.
juniSysClockAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the system clock application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when new frequency and offset error obejects support were added.

juniSysClockAgentV3.name: juniSysClockAgentV3
juniSysClockAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the system clock component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the system clock component is supported in JUNOSe 4.1.2,
        5.0.2 and subsequent system releases.
juniSysClockAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the system clock application in JUNOSe.

juniSysClockAgentV4.name: juniSysClockAgentV4
juniSysClockAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the system clock component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the system clock component is supported in JUNOSe 7.0 and 
        subsequent system releases.
juniSysClockAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the system clock application in JUNOSe.
